    • setPartSearchListener

      protected void setPartSearchListener(javafx.scene.control.TextField search, javafx.scene.control.TableView<Part> tableView)
      This method sets up the listeners for the parts search bar. It selects a specific part with the given ID if the search bar contains only numbers. Otherwise, it filters the parts table by the search bar text. If the search bar is empty, it displays all parts. If the search bar text doesn't match any part, it displays an error message.
